!! 🧮 Math.js Widget

[img[https://img.shields.io/badge/status-experimental-orange]]

This project is under active development and is not production-ready.

Expect breaking changes, unstable behavior, and ongoing API adjustments.

!! 📌 Overview

A lightweight TiddlyWiki widget integrating Math.js for inline expression evaluation.

!! ⚙️ Features

!!! 🌍 Locale-aware parsing
* FR/EN numeric formats
* auto-detection

!!! 🧮 Math.js engine
* arithmetic
* functions (sin, cos, sqrt, log)
* fractions
* units (basic support)

!!! 📐 Scientific notation

<$codeblock>
<$calc scientific="auto">0.00000012</$calc>
</$codeblock>

Modes:
* auto
* always
* never

!!! 🇫🇷 French formatting
* 1 000 000 spacing
* decimal comma support
* × 10^n scientific style

!!! ⚡ Performance
* LRU cache
* lazy evaluation
* optimized refresh cycle

!!! 🔒 Safety
* expression sandboxing
* function whitelist
* avoids unsafe JS access

---

!! 🧩 Usage

!!! Basic

<$codeblock>
<$calc>1 + 2 * 3</$calc>
</$codeblock>

!!! Locale control

<$codeblock>
<$calc in="auto">1,2 × 10^3</$calc>
</$codeblock>

Options:
* auto
* fr-FR
* en-US

!!! Output control

<$codeblock>
<$calc out="fr-FR">1234.56</$calc>
</$codeblock>

!!! Scientific mode

<$codeblock>
<$calc scientific="always">0.00000012</$calc>
</$codeblock>

---

!! 📦 Installation

# Copy plugin into TiddlyWiki plugins folder `./plugins`
# Enable plugin in `tiddlywiki.info`
# Reload wiki

Or 

# Drag and Drop

